Data.name: MPTTestPlan FNC NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in (MILES4ALL-9666)

Data.name: CtrlTestsInTestPlanAllButPASS FNC NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC NL', 'TODO|EXECUTING|FAIL|ABORTED|BLOCKED') ORDER BY rank

Data.name: CtrlTestsInTestPlanAllTODO FNC NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC NL', TODO) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: CtrlTestsInTestPlanAllTODOUnassigned FNC NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC NL', TODO, __NULL__) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: CtrlTestsInTestPlanFAIL FNC NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC NL', FAIL) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: CtrlTestsInTestPlanNoEvidence FNC NL
Data.description: All Tests in FNC NL Test Plan without Test Evidence
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND ((issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC NL', PASS, '', 'true', '', 'true', 'false')) OR (issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC NL', PASS, '', 'true', '', 'false', 'false')) OR (issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC NL', PASS, '', 'false', '', 'true', 'false')) OR (issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC NL', PASS, '', 'false', '', 'false', 'false')))

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlan FNC NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC NL') AND (component is EMPTY OR component = MRI) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanFFlag1Open FNC NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC NL') AND (component is EMPTY OR component = MRI) AND Labels in (eSignature) AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanFFlag1OpenCritical FNC NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC NL') AND (component is EMPTY OR component = MRI) AND Labels in (eSignature) AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) AND Priority = Critical ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanRegressionOpen FNC NL

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanRemainingOpen FNC NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlanRemaining FNC NL') AND (component is EMPTY OR component = MRI) AND (labels not in (eSignature) OR labels is EMPTY) AND Status not in (Closed, Resolved) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanRemainingOpenCritical FNC NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlanRemaining FNC NL') AND (component is EMPTY OR component = MRI) AND (labels not in (eSignature) OR labels is EMPTY) AND Status not in (Closed, Resolved) AND Priority = Critical ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testPlanTestExecutions('MPTTestPlan FNC NL') ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTTestExecsInTestPlanAssignedToCurrentUser FNC NL
Data.description: Executions in Test Plan for current user
Data.jql: filter=270732 AND issue in testExecWithTestRunsAssignedToUser() ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTTestExecsInTestPlanRegression FNC NL
Data.description: Get all Executions related to the tests from Test repo and filter only the ones of the current Test Plan
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testTestExecutions('MPTTestsInTestPlanRegression FNC NL') AND issue in testPlanTestExecutions('MPTTestPlan FNC NL') ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTTestExecsInTestPlanRemaining FNC NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testTestExecutions('MPTTestsInTestPlanRemaining FNC NL') AND issue in testPlanTestExecutions('MPTTestPlan FNC NL') ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTTestExecsInTestPlanUnassignedTODO FNC NL
Data.description: All Test Executions containing Unassigned Tests
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testTestExecutions('CtrlTestsInTestPlanAllTODOUnassigned FNC NL', TODO) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTTestsInTestPlan FNC NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC NL') ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTTestsInTestPlanAssignedToCurrentUserPASSNoEvidence FNC NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND (issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlanAssignedToCurrentUser FNC NL', PASS, '', 'true', '', '', 'false') OR issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlanAssignedToCurrentUser FNC NL', PASS, '', 'false', '', '', 'false'))

Data.name: MPTTestsInTestPlanFFlag1 FNC NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC NL') AND Labels in (eSignature) ORDER BY rank
